Revision history for Device-RadioThermostat

0.04  2016-07-02 21:17:58 EDT
        - Better CT-80 Support (humidity & messages) from Timo Kokkonen (tjko) #2
        - ensure ints are ints not strings in generated JSON from tjko #2

0.03  2013-12-29 02:33:59 EST
        - Lots of good stuff contributed by Philip Gladstone:
        - Support older Perl 5.8
        - get_uuid support
        - find_all method to auto-discover RTCoA thermostats on the network

0.02  2013-09-10 22:06:25 EDT
        - Add datalog method
        - implement clear_message which was in the POD but left out of the code
        - remove leftover use Data::Printer in the module
        - Indicate that the links for API docs are links to a pdf

0.01  2013-09-09 23:17:45 EDT
        - Initial release
